- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses using reinforcement learning (RL) to train dialog models. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper discusses different dialog planning and generation methods. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is relevant as the paper evaluates the simulators using human ratings and interactions.
